name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.

NID 6 is 'ChakraPetch-ExtraLight', Everything looks good.

Chakra Petch ExtraLight Regular (ChakraPetch-ExtraLight.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'ChakraPetch-ExtraLight', Everything looks good.

Pass

Chakra Petch ExtraLight Regular (ChakraPetch-ExtraLight.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Chakra Petch' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraLight' = NID 1 'Chakra Petch ExtraLight'.

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Chakra Petch' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraLight Italic' = NID 1 'Chakra Petch ExtraLight' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Chakra Petch Light Regular (ChakraPetch-Light.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'ChakraPetch-Light', Everything looks good.

Pass

Chakra Petch Light Regular (ChakraPetch-Light.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Chakra Petch' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light' = NID 1 'Chakra Petch Light'.

Pass

Chakra Petch Light Italic (ChakraPetch-LightItalic.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'ChakraPetch-LightItalic', Everything looks good.

Pass

Chakra Petch Light Italic (ChakraPetch-LightItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'ChakraPetch-LightItalic', Everything looks good.

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Chakra Petch' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light Italic' = NID 1 'Chakra Petch Light' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Chakra Petch Regular (ChakraPetch-Regular.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'ChakraPetch-Regular', Everything looks good.

Pass

Mac NID 6

NID 6 is 'ChakraPetch-Medium', Everything looks good.

Chakra Petch Medium Regular (ChakraPetch-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Chakra Petch' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium' = NID 1 'Chakra Petch Medium'.

Pass

Chakra Petch Medium Italic (ChakraPetch-MediumItalic.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'ChakraPetch-MediumItalic', Everything looks good.

Chakra Petch Medium Italic (ChakraPetch-MediumItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'ChakraPetch-MediumItalic', Everything looks good.

Pass

Chakra Petch Medium Italic (ChakraPetch-MediumItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Chakra Petch' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium Italic' = NID 1 'Chakra Petch Medium' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Pass

Chakra Petch SemiBold Regular (ChakraPetch-SemiBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Chakra Petch' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold' = NID 1 'Chakra Petch SemiBold'.

Chakra Petch SemiBold Italic (ChakraPetch-SemiBoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Chakra Petch' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold Italic' = NID 1 'Chakra Petch SemiBold' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Pass

Chakra Petch Bold (ChakraPetch-Bold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'ChakraPetch-Bold', Everything looks good.

Pass

Unless you have entered into a specific license agreement granting you additional rights, your use of this software is limited by the terms of the actual license agreement you have entered into with Monotype. You may not copy or distribute this software. If you have any questions concerning your rights you should review the license agreement you received with the software.
